SELECT
    :batchDate   AS sday,
    :batchDate   AS eday,
    'DUFX0005.D' AS flnm,
    convert(varchar(8),
            getdate() AT TIME ZONE 'UTC' AT TIME ZONE 'Taipei Standard Time',
            112) AS sysdy,
    replace(convert(varchar(8),
                    getdate() AT TIME ZONE 'UTC' AT TIME ZONE 'Taipei Standard Time',
                    108),
            ':',
            '')  AS systm,
    COUNT(*)     AS totcnt
FROM
    botsrdb.db_fbkbal_dds f
WHERE
    f.db_fbkbal_txdate = :batchDate
